         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Verso, Greek text);;(Cross) D.V. account regarding the shipment of barley of the monastery of [Apa] Thomas:;from the ktema of Paas: 20 artabai;;from the ktema of Phase: 16 artabai;;from the ktema of Neolakkos: 20 artabai;;from the ktema of Kalasirios: 18 artabai;;from the ktema of Psarakole: 14 artabai;;Parob, son of Kauch(--): 15 artabai;;from the ktema of Nesieeu(--): 7 artabai;;from Apollinopolis: 11 1/2 artabai;;Dioskoria: [[5]] 6 artabai;;Terot from the ktema of Pampas: 15 artabai</ab>
         </div>
